name: Noetic Digital
description:
For organisations that need fast, affordable and accurate research, Noetic enables a collaborative relationship with their market; turning insight into action and enabling more informed, less biassed decision-making. 
(Imagine an AI agent that bridges your company and market, acting as your customers' voice.)
